*** How to Automation suite for API Testing using Postman ***

We can all the requests in collections and using Tests console we can print pass message and run the collection at once.



Rest Assured.

-Java lib(api) for testing RESTful web services
-To Test XML or JSON based web services
-Supports POST,get,put,delete,etc.
- Can be integrated with testing frameworks like JUnits,TestNG
- Rest Assured is implemented in Groovy language.

-we can create tests using BDD style (When, given etc keywords)

Website - https://rest-assured.io/

#-Pre-Requistes
- Java
- IDE(eclipse)
- Maven
- TestNG(for creating testing framework)


Steps-
-Create new Maven Project
- Goto - https://mvnrepository.com/ for Rest Assured dependency
<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.rest-assured/rest-assured -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.rest-assured</groupId>
    <artifactId>rest-assured</artifactId>
    <version>4.3.2</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

- get Testng dependency
 <dependency>
    <groupId>org.testng</groupId>
    <artifactId>testng</artifactId>
    <version>7.3.0</version>
    <scope>test</scope>
</dependency>

- we also need Apache poi for data driven project (for Later)
https://mvnrepository.com/search?q=apache+poi

- 
